{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.repeatAndRfl\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">repeatAndRfl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Solves conjunctions whose leaves are `True` or `e₁ = e₂`, and returns a residual goal containing\nexactly the conjuncts that could not be solved.\nThis procedure may assign metavariables in `e₁`/`e₂`, for example for `e = ?m` it will assign\n`?m := e`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.repeatAndRfl","kind":"opaque","line":106,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.repeatAndRfl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L106-L144"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsSimp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">introsSimp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mvarId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">errorMsg</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Simplify the forall telescope of the target using `Sym.Simp.simpTelescope`,\nthen introduce all binders via `Sym.intros`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsSimp","kind":"def","line":92,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introsSimp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L92-L104"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.simpTargetTelescope\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">simpTargetTelescope</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">mvarId</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> (<a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.simpTargetTelescope","kind":"def","line":79,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.simpTargetTelescope","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L79-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.processHypotheses\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">processHypotheses</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Goal\">Meta.Grind.Goal</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`Grind.processHypotheses` if `Context.internalize` is `true`, otherwise a no-op. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.processHypotheses","kind":"def","line":75,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.processHypotheses","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L75-L77"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.applyChecked\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">BackwardRule</span>.<span class=\"name\">applyChecked</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">rule</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule\">Meta.Sym.BackwardRule</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ruleDesc?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.ApplyResult\">Meta.Sym.ApplyResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`VCGenM` wrapper around `BackwardRule.apply`. Behaves identically to\n`rule.apply goal` unless the application fails and `Context.debug` is on.\nIn that case it retries on a fresh metavariable whose type is the\n`unfoldReducible`-normalized goal type. If the retry succeeds, an earlier\nstep forgot a normalization; we throw a hard error pointing at the rule and\nthe missing reduction.\n\n`ruleDesc?` describes the rule for debug output. When `none`, the description\nis reconstructed from `rule.expr.getAppFn` — works for the common case of a\nconstant rule. Pass a custom message for dynamically-built rules.\n\nDesigned for dot notation: `rule.applyChecked goal`. Requires\n`open Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal` in scope so that the dot lookup resolves.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.applyChecked","kind":"def","line":29,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule.applyChecked","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Util.lean#L29-L68"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Reduce","Lean.Meta.Sym.AlphaShareBuilder","Lean.Meta.Sym.Intro","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Telescope","Lean.Meta.Sym.Util","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Main"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Util"}